videos.description: Louisville's Sam Fuehring knocks down the 3-pointer. Georgia Tech then turns it over, which leads to an easy layup by Asia Durr.
videos.headline: Louisville gets the 3, then steals the ball away for a layup

videos.description: Asia Durr finishes the tough layup with the contact to extend Louisville's lead early in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Durr goes through the defender and scores
